pkgmetadata.longdescription: A Batch Process for High Dimensional Imputation // A correlation- based batch process for fast, accurate imputation for high dimensional missing data problems via chained random forests. See Waggoner (2023) doi:10.1007/s00180-023-01325-9 for more on 'hdImpute', Stekhoven and Bhlmann (2012) doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btr597 for more on 'missForest', and Mayer (2022) https://github.com/mayer79/missRanger for more on 'missRanger'.
